MaterialDialogBuilder - Class in de.mrapp.android.dialog
A builder, which allows to create dialogs, which are designed according to Android 5.0's Material Design guidelines even on pre-Lollipop devices.

Creates a new builder, which allows to create dialogs, which are designed according to Android 5.0's Material Design guidelines even on pre-Lollipop devices.
